<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PeruTM5.3">
<l>mīṉōkku nīḷvayalcūḻ viṟṟuvakkōṭ ṭammāveṉ</l>
<l>pālnōkkā yākilumuṉ paṟṟallāṟ paṟṟillēṉ</l>
<l>tāṉōkkā tettuyarañ ceytiṭiṉun tārvēntaṉ</l>
<l>kōlnōkki vāḻuṅ kuṭipōṉṟi runtēṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O Lord of Viṟṟuvakkōṭu surrounded by vast paddy-fields, which the fish watch!</l>
<l>Even though You will not look in my direction,</l>
<l>I have no attachment other than attachment for You.</l>
<l>I have been like the subjects who live looking up to the sceptre of the garlanded king,</l>
<l rend="indent">whatever the grief he gives [them] by not looking after [them].</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
